en_117973_0	A suspect has been taken into custody along with 13 counterfeit notes of the 5,000 rupee denomination.
en_117973_1	The arrest was made in the Pettah area.
en_117973_2	The Police arrested the suspects from Bastian Mawatha based on a tip off received from a bus conductor.
en_117973_3	The bus conductor had informed the Police over the suspicious note, when the suspect tried to change a 5,000 rupee counterfeit note from him.
en_117973_4	Accordingly the Police apprehended the suspect with thirteen 5,000 rupee counterfeit notes.
en_117973_5	The 39-year-old suspect is a resident of Ampara.
en_117973_6	The suspect has been handed over to the CID for further investigations.
